This folder contains the code on how to use the excellent {ggplot2} extension {ggalluvial} and the excellebt {parcats} for interactive flow diagrams.
In the code we leverage the gapminder dataset and illustrate the ASIA insights namely:
1952: A massive segment was trapped in <45 years life expectancy and <$1k GDP.
2007: That same flow has surged into the 60-74 age bracket and the $5k-$15k income tier.

